description: On the doorstep of Castle Island and the SB beaches, this sun-filled residence is nestled in an upscale development offering a blend of sophistication and unparalleled convenience, with two garage parking spaces. The location provides easy access to the Financial District/Seaport and the airport. Across the threshold, you'll find an open floor plan with a gourmet kitchen featuring European-inspired cabinetry, top-tier Bosch appliances, and striking Calacatta Gold quartz countertops anchored by a spacious island. The two spacious bedrooms include a luxury primary suite with a marble en-suite, dual vanity, and radiant heated floors for ultimate comfort. Unique to this home are upgraded Elfa closets, electronic window treatments, and a deck off the living area. Other details/amenities include floor-to-ceiling windows, in-unit laundry, engineered walnut flooring, shared green space, and extra storage in the garage. This haven is a testament to elegance and refined living.
